md:
giải nghĩa từ "finals" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

Finals /ˈfaɪnəlz/ (noun)

* Meaning: the last stage of a competition, especially a sports competition
* Example: The team made it to the finals of the championship.
* Related words: semifinals, quarterfinals, championship, competition

Finals /ˈfaɪnəlz/ (noun)

* Meaning: the last examinations or tests of a school or university course
* Example: The students are preparing for their finals.
* Related words: exam, test, course, semester

Note: The word "finals" can have different meanings depending on the context. In the first example, it refers to the last stage of a competition, while in the second example, it refers to the last examinations or tests of a school or university course.
